snippet.title: IARC Surrogacy
snippet.description:
The International Assisted Reproduction Center (IARC) is located in Maple Grove, Minnesota, U.S.A., but our assisted reproduction programs span the globe. 

We realize you are coming to us after a long struggle with fertility problems, and, despite the heroic efforts of many, you continue to search for a child. Our staff believes in every parent wanting to experience the fulfillment, joy, and challenge of parenthood should be given the opportunity to do so. We would like to help you achieve that goal. We are committed to providing personalized, informative, and organized service to all our clients.

Our caring staff members will coordinate all aspects of your surrogacy program, including the educational, legal, medical psychological, financial and insurance issues. We have multilingual staff available. We are unique among surrogacy programs in so many ways. Our extremely personalized programs include on-staff personnel who take care of everything for you.
